K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:190b-7: yul der pha rol gyi dpung mi 'jug go /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:190b-8: 'jug na yang de dag la rgyal po chen po rnam thos kyi bu bgegs byed par 'gyur te bgegs sna tshogs brgya dag dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:190b-9: bgegs sna tshogs stong dag byed par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:190b-10: mi'i rgyal po de dag gang dang gang du 'gro ba de dang der rig sngags kyi rgyal mo chen mo rgyal ba can zhes bya ba 'di rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la btags te mdun du gzhag par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:190b-12: adgra chen po dang 'thab pa der yang rig sngags kyi rgyal mo chen mo rgyal ba can zhes bya ba 'di mgul du btags te g-yul ngor zhugs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:190b-13: der rgyal po chen po rnam thos kyi bus pha rol gyi dmag tshogs de la gnod pa 'dis gnod pa byed do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:190b-15: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo chen mo rgyal ba can zhes bya ba 'di su'i mgul du thogs pa de ni /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:191a-8: de rig sngags kyi rgyal mo chen mo rgyal ba can 'di bklags nas der rgyal po chen po rnam thos kyi bu tshogs kyi g-yog 'khor dang bcas te gnod sbyin bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag du ma dang lhan cig tu nad 'go ba dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:191a-10: de nas bcom ldan 'das la gsang ba pa'i bdag po lag na rdo rjes 'di skad ces gsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:191a-12: 'di'i god na rig sngags ches stobs dang ldan pa'am /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:191a-18: rig sngags thams cad kyi mchog lags so //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:192b-20: sems can chen po sems can thams cad la phan pa byed pa khyod yang legs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:192b-21: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo chen mo rgyal ba can 'dis su la srung ba byas pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:192b-25: bde legs su 'gyur ba byas pa de'i lus la mtshon gyis mi tshugs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:192b-30: rims nad nas gdon thams cad kyi bar gyis de la mi tshugs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:193a-0: pha rol gyi gnod pas 'chi ba'i dus byed par mi @193a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:193a-2: rig sngags kyi rgyal mo chen mo rgyal ba can 'di ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:193a-3: de bzhin gshegs pa'i phyag rgyas btab pa yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:193a-5: khyod kyis rig sngags kyi rgyal mo chen mo rgyal ba can zhes bya ba 'di zungs shig /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:193a-13: de'i tshe rig sngags kyi rgyal mo chen mo rgyal ba can 'di sems kyi rgyud mi mnyam pa; mi bzad pa'i sems dang ldan pa de dag dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-016:193a-14: sems can sdang ba thams cad kyi don dang /
